# TAMAC Inc. — Source of Truth

> **Capstone:** Secure, highly available enterprise network in Cisco Packet Tracer  
> **Company:** TAMAC Inc. (e-commerce aggregator) · **Employees:** 200–250 · **Platform:** Packet Tracer

---

## Hard rules (always enforce)

1. **No Procurement department** — never VLAN 60, `192.168.60.0/26`, or Procurement ports.
2. **Eight departments:** Executive, IT, Operations, Finance, Customer Service, Marketing, HR, Guest.
3. **Built reality wins** — if design docs conflict with [docs/PROGRESS.md](docs/PROGRESS.md) or [docs/logs/](docs/logs/), follow what we actually configured.
4. **Log major milestones** — update PROGRESS.md + add a file under `docs/logs/`.

