## Quick reference

### Topology

```
[ ISP-Router ] --Serial-- [ 2911 Edge Router ]
                              | Gi0/0 (trunk: 90, 200)
                         [ 3560 CORE-SW ]-- Fa0/1 -- [ DNS-SVR ]
                           /  |  |  \
                      IDF   IDF  IDF  IDF
                      1-A  1-B  2-A  2-B
```

### Departments → VLAN

| Dept | VLAN | Gateway |
|---|---|---|
| Executive | 10 | 192.168.10.1 |
| Finance | 20 | 192.168.20.1 |
| Operations | 30 | 192.168.30.1 |
| Customer Service | 40 | 192.168.40.1 |
| IT | 50 | 192.168.50.1 |
| HR | 70 | 192.168.70.1 |
| Marketing | 80 | 192.168.80.1 |
| Guest | 90 | **192.168.90.1** (Edge Router Gi0/0.90) |
| Servers | 100 | 192.168.100.1 |
| Management | 200 | 192.168.200.1 |

### Implemented key IPs (Packet Tracer)

| Device | IP | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Core SVI (MGMT) | 192.168.200.1/28 | Default gw for mgmt VLAN |
| Edge Router LAN | **192.168.200.14/28** | Gi0/0.200 subif; core Fa0/8 **trunk** 90,200 |
| Guest gateway | **192.168.90.1/25** | Gi0/0.90 subif; GUEST_RESTRICT ACL |
| DNS-SVR | 192.168.100.2/28 | Core Fa0/1 access VLAN 100 |
| Edge Router WAN | 10.0.0.2/30 | Serial to ISP |

> Router uses `.14` not `.254` — `/28` only allows `.1`–`.14`.

### Core switch ports (3560-24PS — only 2× Gigabit)

| Core port | Connects to |
|---|---|
| Fa0/8 | Edge Router Gi0/0 (trunk VLANs 90, 200) |
| Fa0/1 | DNS-SVR |
| Gi0/1–2 | IDF 1-A (Po1) |
| Fa0/2–3 | IDF 1-B (Po2) |
| Fa0/4–5 | IDF 2-A (Po3) |
| Fa0/6–7 | IDF 2-B (Po4) |

